# Output Format

Produce a **Features Request** document in the following markdown format:

```markdown
# Features Request
## Feature: [F001] <name>
### Description
<detailed description of what this feature does and why>
### Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] <criterion 1>
- [ ] <criterion 2>
### Dependencies
- <dependency on other features, if any>
### Priority
<high/medium/low>
```

Every acceptance criterion must be specific and testable. Dependencies should reference feature IDs. Priority should reflect both user value and implementation order.
